Portfolio Companies




 

REIT Investment Group, LLC fulfills and maintains the necessary 100 shareholder requirement for private REITs.




 

ICG Captive Services provides consulting and management services to entities that form captives.




 

Commerce Insurance, an affiliate of ICG Captive Services, is a protected cell captive company formed to function as a pooling facility for various participant captives.




 

Iroquois Merchant Services provides payment processing solutions including credit card processing, merchant cash advance/line of credit, gift and loyalty card programs, electronic check acceptance and related business solutions for businesses, government entities, non-profits, and schools.




 

Iroquois Financial Partners II, LP invests in growth-stage companies through a variety of debt structures.




 

RIG Holdings invests in real estate projects in major US markets through a variety of structures.




 

Covenant Surgical Partners acquires and manages single and limited-specialty ambulatory surgery centers across the United States.




 

Iroquois Investment Banking provides a full complement of investment banking services to lower middle market clients in a diverse range of industries.
 





