 ICG’s Approach

“We understand the complexity of combining various types of financing alternatives and can assist clients to create the appropriate solution for both short term needs and long term success.”
As a team, we seek to use our combined operating and transaction advisory experience to develop solutions tailored to the needs of our clients. We deploy both short term and long term debt capital, as well as, equity capital, to assist our clients in achieving their financial objectives. We have the unique ability to meet the diverse needs of all our clients.
We typically help management teams finance their companies. This is usually done in one of two ways:

Investing our own capital alongside and on the same terms as our high net worth investor base; or
Applying our investment banking expertise to raise capital from lenders or investors

We understand the complexity of combining various types of financing alternatives and can assist clients to create the appropriate solution for both short term needs and long term success. We will shoulder the burden throughout the financing process and create a partnership that enables management to concentrate on day-to-day operations.
Why choose Iroquois?

We are led by business professionals with extensive operating, finance and merger and acquisition experience
Individual investors take comfort in the fact that we invest our own money in our businesses and on the same terms as they do
We are able to raise capital from our individual investor base for the businesses in our portfolio
We work with senior management to develop both an operating strategy and capital plan for growing the company’s business and creating value for its shareholders
By utilizing the experience of our founders and principals, we help senior management teams find the best financial solutions for their companies
We are an active merchant banking partner for your business

Extensive Operating Experience

Our team includes CEOs and CFOs of businesses ranging from startups to multi-billion dollar NYSE companies
We have a successful track record as operators of portfolio companies
Our advisory board has diverse management experience

Experienced Management Team

We have extensive experience at many different types and sizes of companies and firms
Our dedicated team of professionals work together for each client
We are financial services and health care focused

Access to Alternative Sources of Capital

Our firm’s own capital
High net worth investor base
Iroquois Financial Partners

 


